{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/quangv/awesome-couchdb/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9ecba482-f5d4-5a3a-a902-e57cfb9ed7bc","html":"<p>\n  <br>\n  <img width=\"300\" src=\"https://rawgit.com/quangv/awesome-couchdb/master/logo--couch.png\" alt=\"awesome couchdb logo\">\n  <br>\n</p>\n<h1 id=\"awesome-couchdb-awesome-prs-welcome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-couchdb-awesome-prs-welcome\" aria-label=\"awesome couchdb awesome prs welcome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome CouchDB <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a> <a href=\"http://makeapullrequest.com\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/PRs-welcome-brightgreen.svg?style=flat-square\" alt=\"PRs Welcome\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A curated meta resources &#x26; best practices list for CouchDB.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://couchdb.apache.org/\">CouchDB</a></strong> is a document-oriented NoSQL database that syncs.</p>\n<p>Pull-Requests are welcomed.</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenod