9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>News &#x26; Blog Posts</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.garrensmith.com/blogs/mini-couch-hack-week\">MiniCouchDB in Rust</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.couchdb.org/2020/02/26/the-road-to-couchdb-3-0-prepare-for-4-0/\">The Road to CouchDB 3.0: Prepare for 4.0</a> <em>(02-26-2020)</em></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"patterns--best-practices\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#patterns--best-practices\" aria-label=\"patterns  best practices permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Patterns &#x26; Best Practices</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://ehealthafrica.github.io/couchdb-best-practices/\">Best Practices</a> - Best Practices, eHealth Africa.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pouchdb.com/2014/04/14/pagination-strategies-with-pouchdb.html\">Pagination strategies with PouchDB </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pouchdb.com/2014/06/17/12-pro-tips-for-better-code-with-pouchdb.html\">12 pro tips for better code with PouchDB</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/assafmo/couchdb-linux-performance\">Linux tuning for better CouchDB performance</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/assafmo/couchdb-linux-performance\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">30</span></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"mapreduce\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mapreduce\" aria-label=\"mapreduce permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Map/Reduce</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://pouchdb.com/2014/05/01/secondary-indexes-have-landed-in-pouchdb.html\">PouchDB - Secondary Indexes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cloudant.com/blog/mapreduce-from-the-basics-to-the-actually-useful/#.WIDBfRsrKUl\">Cloudant - MapReduce Primer</a> - Great intro on reduce, group, group_level.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://docs.couchdb.org/en/2.0.0/couchapp/views/joins.html#using-view-collation\">Using View Collation</a> - Index mapping (emits) for data joins.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://docs.couchdb.org/en/2.0.0/couchapp/views/collation.html\">Views Collation</a> - More documentation on \"View Collation\".</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.ibm.com/clouddataservices/docs/cloudant/get-started/mapreduce-and-the-secondary-index/\">Cloudant - MapReduce and the Secondary Index (Video)</a> - Great videos here on mapReduce, secondary indexes, and complex keys.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.cloudant.com/design_documents.html\">Cloudant - Design Documents</a> - Cloudant's documentation is also great resource for learning concepts of CouchDB.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.cloudant.com/design_document_management.html\">Cloudant - Design Document Management</a> - How to manage design doc changes in production.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"joins\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#joins\" aria-label=\"joins permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Joins</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://docs.couchdb.org/en/2.0.0/couchapp/views/joins.html#joins-with-views\">Joins with Views</a> - Must read for understanding approach on doing efficient joins for CouchDB/PouchDB.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.cloudant.com/transactions.html\">Grouping related documents together in Cloudant</a> - An approach that leverages CouchDB high availability nature.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"document-versioning\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#document-versioning\" aria-label=\"document versioning permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Document Versioning</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wiki.apache.org/couchdb/Document_revisions?action=show&#x26;redirect=DocumentRevisions\">Document Revisions (from wiki)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20100701165612/http://blog.couch.io/post/632718824/simple-document-versioning-with-couchdb\">Simple Document Versioning</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"blogs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#blogs\" aria-label=\"blogs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Blogs</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.couchdb.org/\">Official Blog</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"docs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#docs\" aria-label=\"docs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Docs</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://docs.couchdb.org/\">Official Docs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wiki.apache.org/couchdb/Frequently_asked_questions\">FAQ (old wiki)</a> - Seems to have more faqs than the <a href=\"https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/COUCHDB/Frequently+Asked+Questions\">new wiki</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"books\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#books\" aria-label=\"books permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Books</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://guide.couchdb.org/\">The Definitive Guide</a> - CouchDB's <em>\"Dog\"</em> Book.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/COUCHDB/Books\">List of books on the Wiki</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"videos\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#videos\" aria-label=\"videos permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Videos</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BKQ9kXKoHS810\">10 Common Misconceptions</a> - More videos from this <a href=\"http://conf.couchdb.org/\">conference</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://nosqltapes.com\">The NoSQL Tapes</a> - CouchDB is discussed on <a href=\"http://nosqltapes.com/video/hoffman-and-kocoloski-on-cloudant-and-couchdb\">Volume 5 - CouchDB</a>, <a href=\"http://nosqltapes.com/video/understanding-mapreduce-with-mike-miller\">Volume 8 - MapReduce</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.oreilly.com/pub/e/1760\">Scaling Out with BigCouch</a> -